this?

00:18:08.760 --> 00:18:10.709
You look like a primitive man.”

00:18:10.709 --> 00:18:13.009
He said, “I want to be primitive.”

00:18:13.009 --> 00:18:14.959
I said, “You cannot.

00:18:14.959 --> 00:18:16.610
Your brain is modern.

00:18:16.610 --> 00:18:20.399
By just making such hair, are you going to
become primitive?

00:18:20.399 --> 00:18:23.019
You cannot become primitive.”

00:18:23.019 --> 00:18:27.000
But just imagine, all these external things
they do.

00:18:27.000 --> 00:18:28.050
For what?

00:18:28.050 --> 00:18:30.680
To have an identity.

00:18:30.680 --> 00:18:38.060
Now this idea of identity is also is a sign
that you do not have your maryadas.

00:18:38.060 --> 00:18:39.060
You can do anything.

00:18:39.060 --> 00:18:42.300
You can become a punk and all kinds of things
you do.

00:18:42.300 --> 00:18:45.060
I mean, there are no maryadas.

00:18:45.060 --> 00:18:48.180
And that means you are denying Ganesha completely.

00:18:48.180 --> 00:18:56.130
Ganesha has created those maryadas innately
within us.

00:18:56.130 --> 00:19:01.300
Even a prostitute in India, if she has to
take to that profession because she’s forced

00:19:01.300 --> 00:19:07.180
into it, maybe she’s been brought from somewhere
or maybe that out of her big problems she

