taking beer sometimes.”

00:24:17.800 --> 00:24:26.709
After that, I didn’t know where to look
and what to say.

00:24:26.734 --> 00:24:32.940
Very seriously he said, “You are Mother,
so I must confess to You, but now I will never

00:24:32.940 --> 00:24:34.001
touch beer.”

00:24:34.026 --> 00:24:35.510
Imagine.

00:24:35.510 --> 00:24:41.590
Very seriously he was talking, and another
fellow came, he has told Me.

00:24:41.590 --> 00:24:45.360
I said, “Now you Indians don’t want to
come to this thing.

00:24:45.360 --> 00:24:46.360
What is it?

00:24:46.360 --> 00:24:47.570
You are all making money?”

00:24:47.570 --> 00:24:52.060
He said, “We have made a lot of money here
and we don’t want any money.”

00:24:52.060 --> 00:24:54.190
But I said, “Then why don’t you come?

00:24:54.190 --> 00:24:57.100
You should come and take your, to Sahaja Yoga.

00:24:57.100 --> 00:24:58.100
Why not?”

00:24:58.100 --> 00:25:02.230
He said, “You see, Mother, mostly the trouble
is…”

00:25:02.230 --> 00:25:06.420
With very great hesitation, he said that,
“You see, mostly it is not advertised in

00:25:06.420 --> 00:25:11.800
Indian papers, and we Indians think that we
are rather of a different species, you see,

00:25:11.800 --> 00:25:16.970
how are we going to fit in with these people
because, you see, their ideas are so different,

00:25:16.970 --> 00:25:21.270
ours are so different, and how are we going
to fit in with them?

00:25:21.270 --> 00:25:23.300
It’s very difficult.

00:25:23.300 --> 00:25:28.150
But this time I saw some Indians also and
some Indian musicians singing, so it seems

00:25:28.150 --> 00:25:30.830
that we can fit into them.”

00:25:30.830 --> 00:25:34.310
“Yes,” I said, “They can fit in to you
and you can fit in to them.

00:25:34.310 --> 00:25:35.310
It’s easy.

00:25:35.310 --> 00:25:36.310
They are your style only.”

00:25:36.310 --> 00:25:41.100
He said, “We were really enamored how they
were nice, you see, and they were.”

00:25:41.100 --> 00:25:45.360
Because they do not consider that these things
are bad or anything.

00:25:45.360 --> 00:25:46.760
India is like that, you see.

00:25:46.760 --> 00:25:50.490
They think you are of a different bottle and
they are of a different bottle.

00:25:50.490 --> 00:25:53.670
So you are like that and they are like that.

00:25:53.670 --> 00:25:58.860
They cannot be like you and you cannot be
like them, so they think it is a different

00:25:58.860 --> 00:26:02.480
bottle you belong to, you see, different category
of people.

00:26:02.480 --> 00:26:06.630
But they don’t think that you are bad or
good, they don’t pass judgment.

00:26:06.630 --> 00:26:13.010
But this is what it is, that we have to understand
that we have gone too far with this madness,

00:26:13.010 --> 00:26:15.580
spoiling our Shri Ganesha.

00:26:15.580 --> 00:26:24.740
Also Australians have to give a very big lead
in Shri Ganesha’s area because you are sitting

00:26:24.740 --> 00:26:29.130
on the soil of Shri Ganesha.

00:26:29.130 --> 00:26:31.830
To all the Sahaja yogis, you must show.

00:26:31.830 --> 00:26:38.630
But, as you know what, we had horrible experiences
so far, and how people have been dominating

00:26:38.630 --> 00:26:48.780
and doing all kinds of nonsensical things,
money-wise and otherwise also morality-wise.

00:26:48.780 --> 00:26:57.700
So it sometimes upsets the whole balance of
Sahaja Yoga because it’s all depending on

00:26:57.700 --> 00:27:04.020
Shri Ganesha; that means depending on Australians.

00:27:04.020 --> 00:27:12.280
And Australians have all the possibility of
reaching a great height in Ganesh principle,

00:27:12.280 --> 00:27:16.030
because they have the Mother Earth here sitting
down.

00:27:16.030 --> 00:27:19.120
What else do they want?

00:27:19.120 --> 00:27:22.720
You need not take to stupid American-style
things.

00:27:22.720 --> 00:27:28.260
I mean, if you see their Hallowe’en, I tell
you, you won’t eat your food for eight days.

00:27:28.260 --> 00:27:34.850
And if you go only to Rio, even you do not
visit their carnivals, but even if you see

00:27:34.850 --> 00:27:39.950
the pictures, you won’t eat your food for
one month, so horrible they are.

00:27:39.950 --> 00:27:50.190
So are we going to follow them, or are we
going to start our own Australian Shri Ganesha’s

00:27:50.190 --> 00:27:52.730
special people?

00:27:52.730 --> 00:28:04.640
Or, this I have to warn you, and people are
all watching all over, all Sahaja yogis are

00:28:04.640 --> 00:28:08.040
there; you know that all over the world we
have Sahaja yogis.

00:28:08.040 --> 00:28:15.270
They’re watching everyone, and you have
to do your maximum to express your Ganesh

00:28:15.270 --> 00:28:20.400
principle, which should be very easy for you.

00:28:20.400 --> 00:28:25.070
And as I have told you, that Australia was
a part and parcel of India once upon a time.

00:28:25.070 --> 00:28:27.620
It has come down here.

00:28:27.620 --> 00:28:33.320
So, at least in your films and all that, you
can say they’re dharmic, they are dharmic.

00:28:33.320 --> 00:28:41.830
They’re not so bad as the American films
are, but still this idea of copying the French

00:28:41.830 --> 00:28:46.240
or the Americans shows that we have lost our
personality.

00:28:46.240 --> 00:28:50.290
But Shri Ganesha gives you a personality.

00:28:50.290 --> 00:28:54.090
He gives you your personality, because He
gives you maryadas.

00:28:54.090 --> 00:28:57.170
You see, by maryadas only, you get your personality.

00:28:57.170 --> 00:29:00.200
A person is known by his maryadas.

00:29:00.200 --> 00:29:04.660
And that’s what has to come within us, are
our maryadas.

00:29:04.660 --> 00:29:07.700
So today’s puja is about Shri Ganesha.

00:29:07.700 --> 00:29:13.110
As of course you know, He has got four petals
and you know what He is placed in and what

00:29:13.110 --> 00:29:18.240
He does and all that, and how He looks after
the chastity of His Mother and all that.

00:29:18.240 --> 00:29:25.120
But the main thing is that how we develop
Shri Ganesha within us, how people see us

00:29:25.120 --> 00:29:30.570
as the incarnations of innocence on this Earth.

00:29:30.570 --> 00:29:38.740
I know it’s very difficult, but imagine
Shri Ganesha sitting on the gate of hell,

00:29:38.740 --> 00:29:45.770
of excretion, because He’s just like a lotus,
above everything else, and He makes everything

00:29:45.770 --> 00:29:46.810
fragrant.

00:29:46.810 --> 00:29:53.740
In the same way I expect all of you, the Sahaja
yogis of Australia, to have that beautiful

00:29:53.740 --> 00:30:03.790
personality of Shri Ganesha, and that you
emit that fragrance of innocence among all

00:30:03.790 --> 00:30:06.760
the Sahaja yogis, and then among all the world.

00:30:06.760 --> 00:30:09.968
May God bless you.
